{"type": "article", "id": 4055, "title": "360度旋转支架", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-03T07:31:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233325Ii60ruybhOjs29ln.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>黑胶唱机是旋转的、时钟是旋转的，自行车轮也是旋转的，来自斯洛维尼亚首都卢布尔亚那的设计团队 Luka Pirnat 现在想让你的书架也旋转起来。日前 Luka Pirnat 在众筹网站 Kickstarter 上线了一款名为「360 Shelf」的墙面支架，运用了入墙式的旋转轴设计，使得整个支架可以灵活旋转，整个木质架子的内部边沿做了 45 度斜角的设计，可以供用户放置书本杂志、唱片等东西，还可自行创意用多个小架子装饰墙面或搭建墙面收纳空间。提供原木色、白色、芥末黄以及染色木等 4 种颜色选择，起售价 40 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/lukapirnat/360-shelf-rotating-multiuse-shelf\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>，预计 2015 年 2 月出货。<br>\r\n<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/002/961/055/3270d3a615f4772698409f7c979d4a4a_large.gif?1416826956\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n</p>\n<p>\r\n\t<iframe src=\"http://www.tudou.com/programs/view/html5embed.action?type=0&amp;code=cWVUjembFx4&amp;lcode=&amp;resourceId=0_06_05_99\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"width:640px;height:400px;\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233323fmRuKYDkzUdGcln9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233324GRiWmwZfVdFTPyoO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233324KGevJ079fqjUBman.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233324SVWj5c8C64YPLgiQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}